Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理论有点道理 这名儿可不怎么样 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So Big Bang is in some sense a misnomer but the name stuck.
