Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个理论现在已经是基础理论 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right now Big Bang theory is a solid part of science we understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人硬不接受这个理论 肯定被大家按疯子对待 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Anybody who do not accept it will be regard  by  most of the community as a crackpot.
