Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释宇宙是如何形成的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to explain how our Universe was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙学家说起这个理论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When cosmologists refer to talk about the Big Band theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释的都是爆炸以后的事 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it is really on description of aftermath The Big Band.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理论没有解释\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The conventional Big Bang theory say anything about
