Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的扩展证实了大爆炸理论 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Big Bang is really our evolving, expanding universe.
