Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的故事从地球开始 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the view of the Universe begins with the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是地球 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the Earth.
