Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满生物  每24小时自转一圈 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It teems with life and rotate once every 24 hours
